externalStoreDefault.Description: Information about an external storage location.

encryptionCertBase64.Description: The base64 raw data for the backup encryption certificate.

encryptionCertThumbprint.Description: The thumbprint of the encryption certificate.

backupFrequencyInHours.Description: The interval, in hours, for the frequency that the scheduler takes a backup.

availableCapacity.Description: Free space at the backup location.

isBackupSchedulerEnabled.Description: True if the backup scheduler is enabled.

nextBackupTime.Description: The scheduled time of the next backup.

backupRetentionPeriodInDays.Description: The retention period, in days, for backs in the storage location.
